name: SpongeBob SquarePants
desc: SpongeBob is the main character of the show. He has a very child-like personality.

name: Patrick Star
desc: Patrick is the comic relief character of the show. He is SpongeBob's best friend.

name: Squidward Tentacles
desc: Squidward is the foil for Spongebob. He is very pessimistic by comparison.

name: SpiderMan (Peter)
desc: Peter Parker, also known as Spider-Man, is a young, brilliant scientist and photographer from New York City. After being bitten by a radioactive spider, he gained incredible superpower.

name: SpiderMan (Miles)
desc: Miles Morales is another Spider-Man from New York City. He possesses powers similar to Peter Parker's, having been bitten by a genetically-altered spider.

name: Venom
desc: Venom is an alien. The symbiote grants superhuman strength, agility, and the ability to generate web-like tendrils. However, it often influences its host's behavior, resulting in an anti-hero or villainous persona.

name: Pyke
desc: A renowned harpooner from the slaughter docks of Bilgewater, Pyke should have met his death in the belly of a gigantic jaull-fish… and yet, he returned.

name: Sylas
desc: Raised in one of Demacia’s lesser quarters, Sylas of Dregbourne has come to symbolize the darker side of the Great City.

name: Qiyana
desc: In the jungle city of Ixaocan, Qiyana plots her own ruthless path to the high seat of the Yun Tal.
